{"tid":644451,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"關於我朋友老母既故事","createTime":"2018-04-27T08:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T15:48:55.000Z","uid":147276,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07fb82c4ce1a7329e437b841b38d63539c10796d","tid":644451,"uid":147276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的 同呢個老死都識左十幾年<br />\n細個成日都去佢屋企玩<br />\n佢老母係典型大陸大媽<br />\n講野唔正 大聲 冇文化 食古不化<br />\n<br />\n事件一 有另一個同學A 住我老死下一層<br />\n所以佢地成家都好熟 而老死屋企長期連鐵閘都唔鎖<br />\n淨係關埋左 所以一拉就入到去 <br />\n深知呢個習慣既同學A 一如往常咁上佢屋企<br />\n諗住玩 點知一入到去佢屋企 見到我老死老母<br />\n係度睇AV 因為電腦擺廳 行完走廊就見到<br />\n呢一下佢老母竟然講左句 埋黎一齊睇呀<br />\n返去介紹埋比你老豆老母睇<br />\n<br />\n事件二 我老死話 佢老母由細到大都好鍾意<br />\n對住屋企牆講野 如似同d三姑六婆傾計咁大聲<br />\n我聽到果下都疾撚左 仲要係上年佢先同我講<br />\n佢話有一次 係屋企唔撚見左銀包 <br />\n佢知道一定係屋企唔見左 所以問佢老母<br />\n佢老母話 得啦等陣幫你搵<br />\n然後走出廳 過左陣我老死係房<br />\n就聽到佢老母對住牆問 我呀仔個銀包係邊呀？ <br />\n唔好玩佢啦佢仲細 細路仔唔識世界姐 比返佢啦<br />\n我老死梗係以為佢鳩up啦<br />\n點知過左陣 佢老母就比返個銀包 比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bec2bb4e09a2724b98eee56289fa347038edee3","tid":644451,"uid":147276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"排版好有問題 同我稿打既唔撚同既 屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3599979b519a5161b6bd8e0b1304f9dfbf87d3","tid":644451,"uid":15353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"睇AV關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e1ec215de13148c646c29effc14e6d818dbf2f","tid":644451,"uid":147276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d3599979b519a5161b6bd8e0b1304f9dfbf87d3","tid":644451,"uid":15353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"睇AV關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"本身係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57154481dc587a2a123d599533b56f2a71ad0bf3","tid":644451,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"完?<br />\n<br />\n等我仲期待樓主食人老母重口味包膠"},{"pid":"4ac3b4716a18b0fec50cd3e3d9b748fa34184343","tid":644451,"uid":15353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"有陰陽眼or養鬼仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔明睇av係做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4082b281c8efe5ac0f96c8d33be5c71b641174c","tid":644451,"uid":147276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ac3b4716a18b0fec50cd3e3d9b748fa34184343","tid":644451,"uid":15353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"有陰陽眼or養鬼仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔明睇av係做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"佢比發現 應該係咁既反應咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時我地小5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48116a78228a005c10c701f8a6ec49d855e1b90c","tid":644451,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"頭幾段仲乜9"},{"pid":"766d7b613f400476447a6700626f4fa2af8cd7cf","tid":644451,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:51:28.000Z","msg":"啲大陸女人好難頂㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 接觸唔少"},{"pid":"ffc1509b2f2b6502fdccd0bf51f33c9c7c21c43b","tid":644451,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"人哋識問米<br />\n<br />\n你朋友老母問牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4b02bb49e93f5757bf6aa836f5ce053d059555","tid":644451,"uid":162695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:16:46.000Z","msg":"伯母都唔係咁食古不化啫會分享AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565f36c6da8bc3cac8cfb27c5c16925561330a93","tid":644451,"uid":147276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf4b02bb49e93f5757bf6aa836f5ce053d059555","tid":644451,"uid":162695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:16:46.000Z","msg":"伯母都唔係咁食古不化啫會分享AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"姐係佢睇唔係問題 <br />\n仲要極巨姿態咁邀鳩你仲邀鳩埋你老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a662e1750438e5119a510d099e11ca4984d72cf","tid":644451,"uid":147276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48116a78228a005c10c701f8a6ec49d855e1b90c","tid":644451,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"頭幾段仲乜9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"純粹講佢搞笑野"},{"pid":"630c044fd20d078045584ea765d87e367c4d8821","tid":644451,"uid":147276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"仲有一單突然醒起<br />\n以前我果條村好興踩單車 <br />\n我地成班都踩車返學<br />\n有次我老死架車冇左條key 開唔到個鎖<br />\n架車平時係泊樓下 <br />\n佢老母直接係下面坐左係架車隔離用斧仔<br />\n係咁斬係咁斬 斬左唔知幾耐 終於都斬爆個鎖<br />\n拎返部車 全程我同我老死望撚住<br />\n過程入面好多人行過都以為佢老母偷車<br />\nD保安仲問佢係咪偷車 佢話 <br />\n架車我架我唔見左鎖鑰咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74cd4b3e1ecba8e7d08c9f3d62d5b9211c18b5b","tid":644451,"uid":162695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"但係同空氣講嘢又唔似自言自語咁又幾恐佈"}]}